    "en": {
      "title": "In Moratuwa, the least force was used - the air force",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Air Force has released a statement saying that the Air Force used minimal force to control the hot situation at a fuel station near Moratuwa old bridge.",
        "It is also stated in the announcement that this was caused by the situation when a group of people went to work to get fuel with the help of the given tokens.",
        "The Air Force says that one of the people who used the tokens did not even have a vehicle and he was drunk and was trying to anger the people around him.",
        "The Air Force says that there was an attempt to attack an Air Force member and another person pulled out an ammunition container and verbally abused him.",
        "The statement issued by the Air Force further states that additional troops were called to control the situation and the person who behaved in a row was arrested using minimal force and handed over to the police."
      ],
